OL,3,CWhy the welfare reform row is about so
OL,4,Cmuch more than welfare
OL,6,FAny illusion that this isn't the
OL,7,Fsingle most important driver of
OL,8,Fgovernment decision-making was
OL,9,Fshattered on Monday by the revealed
OL,10,Fcontradiction between its
OL,11,Festablishment of a supposedly
OL,12,Ffundamental review, led by
OL,13,Fdisabilities minister Stephen Timms,
OL,14,Fto shape new criteria for awarding
OL,15,FPersonal Independence Payments, while
OL,16,Fnonetheless sticking with the
OL,17,Fcontradictory stipulation that from
OL,18,FNovember next year no one will be
OL,19,Feligible for PIP, if they don't score
OL,20,Ffour points on one of PIP's existing
OL,21,Fcriteria.
