OL,3,CWhy the welfare reform row is about so
OL,4,Cmuch more than welfare
OL,6,FIt is absurd and illogical to
OL,7,Fcharacterise Timms's review as the
OL,8,Fface of humane reform, while
OL,9,Fsimultaneously saying that this new
OL,10,Ffour-point rule based on existing
OL,11,Fcriteria will willy-nilly come into
OL,12,Feffect next year.
OL,14,FSo what's really going on?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
