OL,3,CWhy the welfare reform row is about so
OL,4,Cmuch more than welfare
OL,6,FThe work and pensions secretary's
OL,7,Funspoken reason for sticking to the
OL,8,Ffour-point reform is that without it,
OL,9,Fand under the OBR-assessed fiscal
OL,10,Frules, Reeves would have to fill a
OL,11,F#5bn hole in her finances in the
OL,12,Fautumn budget, and not the #2.5bn hole
OL,13,Fcreated by Kendall's partial welfare-
OL,14,Freform climb down.
OL,16,FThat is a big difference when it comes
OL,17,Fto any taxes Reeves may have to raise
OL,18,For any spending she may have to cut.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
