OL,3,CWhy the welfare reform row is about so
OL,4,Cmuch more than welfare
OL,6,FSo a growing number of Labour MPs see
OL,7,Fthis subservience to the OBR and the
OL,8,Ffiscal rules as just the stupidest
OL,9,Fmotivation for making Monday's
OL,10,Fdecisions, that affect the lives of
OL,11,Fthe most fragile of UK citizens -
OL,12,Fdecisions that will, on the
OL,13,Fgovernment's own calculations, shift
OL,14,F150,000 vulnerable people into poverty.
